reviewText: In our opinion these are explicite and not porn!  A difference each one of us decides.  I would not want the kids to see these but should they find them I would find them easy to explain.  These show sexual engagements that do not degrade (no embarassing moaning). Nothing new here but a nice "couples night" movie or two.  (Kinda' gives us permission to do what we have been doing!)

If I could, I would NOT give this item any 'stars' at all!!!  The videos are so very cheaply made, and corny; I could hardly watch them. They are NOT helpful at all,  just plain stupid!!  The couples are NOT attractive and are NOT believable.  Please do not waste your money!!
